-- I just keep adding abilities as I change classes and eventually they should 
-- all be in here. Endurance  based skills don't require a 'command' field 
-- because they just use the skill name. For spells you have to specify 
-- "invoke" or "cast" and if it's something like Meijin's Blindfold then
-- you can put "rest;invoke 'meijin blindfold';stand" so that you can do the whole
-- thing.
